## Overview

This project demonstrates an Azure ELT pipeline using Azure Data Factory and Databricks.

The pipeline extracts data from a SQL database, loads it into Azure Data Lake Storage Gen2, and performs transformations in Databricks before storing the results in Delta Lake.

## Architecture

SQL Database → Azure Data Factory → ADLS Gen2 → Databricks → Delta Lake

## Technologies

Azure Data Factory  
Azure Data Lake Storage Gen2  
Databricks  
PySpark  
Delta Lake
